            e2="DDI-MedLine.d113.s3.e2" ddi="false"/>
    </sentence>
    <sentence id="DDI-MedLine.d113.s4" text="Optimal conditions, kinetics, equilibrium, and the mechanism of this acid-catalyzed ethanolysis are reported. "/>
    <sentence id="DDI-MedLine.d113.s5" text="The results raise the possibility that the ethanolysis reaction may occur in the stomach of people who consume alcohol and 3-hydroxy-1,4-benzodiazepine on a regular basis. ">
